               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Laṭīfah-'i Zakāʾīyah by Zakāʾ Allāh ibn Isḥāq ibn Ismāʿīl al-Ṭabīb al-Dihlavī</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85083117 https://lccn.loc.gov/sh85100599 https://lccn.loc.gov/sh2005008277" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_854D-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa" otherLangs="ar">Persian and Arabic </textLang>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_23201">Laṭīfah-'i Zakāʾīyah</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_23201">لطيفهٴ زكائيّه</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Lexicographic selection by <persName key="person_f8055" role="aut">[Ḥakīm al-Ḥukamāʾ Ḥāz̲iq al-Mulk] Zakāʾ Allāh [Khān] ibn Isḥāq ibn Ismāʿīl al-Ṭabīb al-Dihlavī</persName>, based on the <title key="work_23201">Qarābādīn</title> or pharmacopoeia of the author’s father and grandfather. 
                        </p>
                        <p>Partially dated colophon (f. 151v): completed by <persName key="person_f8260" role="scr">ʿAbd Allāh</persName> in <placeName>Shāhjahānābād</placeName>, Saturday, 1257/1841. 
                        </p>
                        <p>Rough nastaʿlīq declining into a hand scarcely legible. 
</p>
                        <p>Dense annotations added at the end. 
</p>
                        <p>Stamped foliation. 
</p>
                        <p>Plain paper dust wrapper. 
</p>
                     </note>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="person_f8055">Zakāʾ Allāh ibn Isḥāq ibn Ismāʿīl al-Ṭabīb al-Dihlavī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" key="person_f8055">زكاء الله ابن اسحٰق ابن اسمٰعيل الطّبيب الدّهلوى</persName>
                     </author>
                  </msItem>
